      • visitJpaCriteriaParameter

        public SqmJpaCriteriaParameterWrapper<?> visitJpaCriteriaParameter(JpaCriteriaParameter<?> expression)
        This is called while performing an inflight parameter collection of parameters for `CriteriaQuery#getParameters`. That method can be called multiple times and the parameters may have changed in between each call - therefore the parameters must be collected dynamically each time. This form simply returns the JpaCriteriaParameter
        Specified by:
        visitJpaCriteriaParameter in interface SemanticQueryWalker<Object>
